Hard Rock Cafe PLC said it has filedfor an initial U.S. offering of 2,240,000 American DepositaryShares representing 11.2 mln Class A ordinary shares.    It said 240,000 of the ADS's will be sold by a currentshareholder.    Lead underwriter is &lt;Drexel Burnham Lambert Inc>.    The company said proceeds will be used for the financing ofadditional restaurants, the expansion of existing restaurantsand retail operations and the repayment of debt. Reuter&#3;